      • ofAKind

        public boolean ofAKind(ResourceType resource,
              int number)

        resource - Resource being queried.
        Returns:

        none
        Post:

      • invertList

        public ResourceList invertList()
        This function will invert the current values of the resource list, such that a negative with become a positive and vice verse. For example, if the resource list contains 1 wood, the list will now contain -1 wood.

      • getRandomResourceFromList

        public ResourceType getRandomResourceFromList()
        This function will return a random resource type that currently stored within the resource list. this function is mainly used when a robber is played and a random resource must be stolen.
        Returns:
        Randomized resource type that is present within the resource list.
